{"ts":"2026-05-17T19:19:21.079Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-er4q"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"pm test --add causes immediate history drift via null timeout_seconds"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Reproduction: in a fresh tracker, `pm create` + `pm test <id> --add 'node scripts/run-tests.mjs test'` triggers history_drift_hash_mismatch immediately. Root cause: `sortTests` in src/core/item/item-format.ts:606 assigns `timeout_seconds: value.timeout_seconds` without coercing null to undefined. After TOON round-trip the field comes back as `null`, so canonicalDocument of the reloaded item produces `{command, scope, timeout_seconds: null}` whereas the patch chain records `{command, scope}` — break of replay parity. Verified by hand on Node 25.9.0 with pm 2026.5.14."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","bug","history","pm-cli","test-command"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-17T19:19:21.079Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-17T19:19:21.079Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"1) Repro sequence (create + test --add) produces history_drift=ok 2) sortTests coerces null->undefined symmetric to file load 3) regression test added"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"70baf1a126543d8692bcab0df7ad73392c77a792d24eb59568d9f4450a17a7e3","message":""}
